genresAdvancedInfo.name: forro manauara
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Forro manauara is a modern take on the traditional Brazilian genre, featuring electronic elements and catchy rhythms. Originating from Manaus, the capital of Amazonas, this genre is characterized by its upbeat tempo and distinctive accordion sound.
